{"tid":812104,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"樓爆近了，你們應當悔改","createTime":"2018-09-09T11:28:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-10T00:44:42.000Z","uid":31320,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"fa3faec572a443b0a6994efd4a80770cb22bb374","tid":812104,"uid":31320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T11:28:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/09/191340_6b4649da54aea9bd0de2511d549a799c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F09%2F191340_6b4649da54aea9bd0de2511d549a799c.png&h=62cff52f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《樓爆的審判》是連登淡友於公元2018年完成的壁畫，源自《聖經》中的最後的審判，或者稱為大審判，是指在樓爆末日之時神會出現，將淡友好友復生並對他們進行裁決，淡友成為永生者，好友會打入地獄<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/09/192627_9c8c978e2d334ba5d7cbc30fe667133a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F09%2F192627_9c8c978e2d334ba5d7cbc30fe667133a.png&h=cfa54194&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n阿門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"319c31d6a9afbb18288ef791e681410fb2005582","tid":812104,"uid":31320,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T12:18:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1efc841c492187c6ce1f06206d442fab2e97bc38","tid":812104,"uid":43146,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T12:46:41.000Z","msg":"業主應賤賣物業贖罪"},{"pid":"c2422fb9842ddd2eacadae153d28b7f187280877","tid":812104,"uid":31320,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1efc841c492187c6ce1f06206d442fab2e97bc38","tid":812104,"uid":43146,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T12:46:41.000Z","msg":"業主應賤賣物業贖罪"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T13:35:04.000Z","msg":"神愛世人，甚至將他的物業濺賣，叫一切看淡的不致滅亡，反得永生。"},{"pid":"13a4bf4790985b84fbd2b486883b7a101abfbbaa","tid":812104,"uid":431